      <title>通用汽车与巴克莱银行签署长期信用卡合作协议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/gm-barclays-sign-long-term-credit-card-partnership-agreement-2024-10-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[通用汽车和巴克莱银行周一表示，双方已签署一项长期信用卡合作协议，让客户在购买新款别克、凯迪拉克和其他通用汽车（包括电动汽车）时赚取和兑换奖励积分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/gm-barclays-sign-long-term-credit-card-partnership-agreement-2024-10-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 10:39:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
